The information to be transmitted may include:
Drillers logs and completion reports of wells drilled or dug for the purpose of producing, testing, or monitoring groundwater;
Geophysical logs of water wells;
Water quality analyses of both organic and inorganic constituents;
Results of all pump, extraction, and injection tests;
Flow determinations of surface discharges of groundwater; and
Any additional data as the Kentucky Geological Survey shall require.
